    * none
    Context variables required for this template:
    Example context (json):
    {
        "categories" : [
            [
               {
                  "catid":"7",
                  "contextid":"1",
                  "catname":"MooDuell Pr\u00e4sentation",
                  "courseid":"50"
               }
            ]
        ]
    }
